idth=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 5h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 12h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 19h16\"></path></svg></button></div></nav></div><div class=\"md:hidden\"><div class=\"staggered-menu-wrapper fixed-wrapper\" style=\"--sm-accent:#ff6b6b\" data-position=\"right\"><div class=\"sm-prelayers\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><div class=\"sm-prelayer\" style=\"background:#B497CF\"></div><div class=\"sm-prelayer\" style=\"background:#5227FF\"></div></div><header class=\"staggered-menu-header\" aria-label=\"Main navigation header\"><div class=\"sm-logo\" aria-label=\"Logo\"><span class=\"sm-logo-img-frame\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><img src=\"/_next/static/media/HUNCHMATE - Logo Pack (2).0xjy2zfzpq5od.png\" alt=\"HunchMate\" class=\"sm-logo-img\" draggable=\"false\"/></span></div><button class=\"sm-toggle\" aria-label=\"Open menu\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"staggered-menu-panel\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"sm-toggle-textWrap\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"sm-toggle-textInner\"><span class=\"sm-toggle-line\">Menu</span><span class=\"sm-toggle-line\">Close</span></span></span><span class=\"sm-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"sm-icon-line\"></span><span class=\"sm-icon-line sm-icon-line-v\"></span></span></button></header><aside id=\"staggered-menu-panel\" class=\"staggered-menu-panel\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><div class=\"sm-panel-inner\"><ul class=\"sm-panel-list\" role=\"list\" data-numbering=\"true\"><li class=\"sm-panel-itemWrap\"><a class=\"sm-panel-item\" href=\"/\" aria-label=\"Go to home page\" data-index=\"1\"><span class=\"sm-panel-itemLabel\">Home</span></a></li><li class=\"sm-panel-itemWrap\"><a class=\"sm-panel-item\" href=\"/events\" aria-label=\"Explore all events\" data-index=\"2\"><span class=\"sm-panel-itemLabel\">Explore Events</span></a></li><li class=\"sm-panel-itemWrap\"><a class=\"sm-panel-item\" href=\"/host-event\" aria-label=\"Create or host an event\" data-index=\"3\"><span class=\"sm-panel-itemLabel\">Host Event</span></a></li><li class=\"sm-panel-itemWrap\"><a class=\"sm-panel-item\" href=\"/contact\" aria-label=\"Open contact page\" data-index=\"4\"><span class=\"sm-panel-itemLabel\">Contact</span></a></li><li class=\"sm-panel-itemWrap\"><a class=\"sm-panel-item\" href=\"/login\" aria-label=\"Go to sign in page\" data-index=\"5\"><span class=\"sm-panel-itemLabel\">Sign In</span></a></li></ul><div class=\"sm-socials\" aria-label=\"Social links\"><h3 class=\"sm-socials-title\">Socials</h3><ul class=\"sm-socials-list\" role=\"list\"><li class=\"sm-socials-item\"><a href=\"https://instagram.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"sm-socials-link\">Instagram</a></li><li class=\"sm-socials-item\"><a href=\"https://linkedin.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"sm-socials-link\">LinkedIn</a></li></ul></div></div></aside></div></div><main class=\"page-transition\" style=\"flex:1\"><div class=\"about-page\"><section class=\"about-hero\"><div class=\"about-hero__mesh\"></div><div class=\"container\"><span class=\"badge badge-accent badge-md \"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-rocket\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 15v5s3.03-.55 4-2c1.08-1.62 0-5 0-5\"></path><path d=\"M4.5 16.5c-1.5 1.26-2 5-2 5s3.74-.5 5-2c.71-.84.7-2.13-.09-2.91a2.18 2.18 0 0 0-2.91-.09\"></path><path d=\"M9 12a22 22 0 0 1 2-3.95A12.88 12.88 0 0 1 22 2c0 2.72-.78 7.5-6 11a22.4 22.4 0 0 1-4 2z\"></path><path d=\"M9 12H4s.55-3.03 2-4c1.62-1.08 5 .05 5 .05\"></path></svg> Our Story</span><h1 class=\"about-hero__title\">Engineered to <span class=\"text-gradient\">Empower</span></h1><p class=\"about-hero__subtitle\">Hunchmate was born from a simple belief — every talented individual deserves a platform to discover opportunities, prove their skills, and earn verifiable recognition.</p></div></section><section class=\"about-mission section\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"about-mission__grid\"><div class=\"about-mission__card glass\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-target about-mission__icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"6\"></circle><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"2\"></circle></svg><h3>Our Mission</h3><p>To democratize access to competitive events and create a transparent credentialing ecosystem that bridges talent with opportunity.</p></div><div class=\"about-mission__card glass\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-lightbulb about-mission__icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M15 14c.2-1 .7-1.7 1.5-2.5 1-.9 1.5-2.2 1.5-3.5A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 1 .2 2.2 1.5 3.5.7.7 1.3 1.5 1.5 2.5\"></path><path d=\"M9 18h6\"></path><path d=\"M10 22h4\"></path></svg><h3>Our Vision</h3><p>A world where every hackathon, workshop, and competition is accessible, verifiable, and leaves participants with lasting, portable credentials.</p></div><div class=\"about-mission__card glass\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-heart about-mission__icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M2 9.5a5.5 5.5 0 0 1 9.591-3.676.56.56 0 0 0 .818 0A5.49 5.49 0 0 1 22 9.5c0 2.29-1.5 4-3 5.5l-5.492 5.313a2 2 0 0 1-3 .019L5 15c-1.5-1.5-3-3.2-3-5.5\"></path></svg><h3>Our Promise</h3><p>We build with empathy, design for inclusivity, and engineer for scale. Every feature serves the participants and organizers who trust us.</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"about-values section-lg\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"section-header\"><span class=\"badge badge-gold badge-md \">Core DNA</span><h2 class=\"section-title\">What Drives Us</h2></div><div class=\"about-values__grid\"><div class=\"about-value glass\"><div class=\"about-value__icon\" style=\"background:var(--color-accent)15;color:var(--color-accent)\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-users\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2\"></path><path d=\"M16 3.128a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.744\"></path><path d=\"M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87\"></path><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"7\" r=\"4\"></circle></svg></div><h3>Equality &amp; Empathy</h3><p>Every participant matters equally. We design with care for diverse needs and backgrounds.</p></div><div class=\"about-value glass\"><div class=\"about-value__icon\" style=\"background:var(--color-success)15;color:var(--color-success)\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-globe\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 2a14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0 20 14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0-20\"></path><path d=\"M2 12h20\"></path></svg></div><h3>Diversity</h3><p>From college campuses to corporate boardrooms — our platform welcomes every kind of innovator.</p></div><div class=\"about-value glass\"><div class=\"about-value__icon\" style=\"background:var(--color-gold)15;color:var(--color-gold)\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-zap\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z\"></path></svg></div><h3>Innovation</h3><p>We don&#x27;t just facilitate innovation — we embody it in every feature we build.</p></div><div class=\"about-value glass\"><div class=\"about-value__icon\" style=\"background:var(--color-purple)15;color:var(--color-purple)\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path></svg></div><h3>Trust &amp; Verification</h3><p>QR-validated entries and unique credential IDs ensure every achievement is verifiable.</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"about-how section-lg\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"section-header\"><span class=\"badge badge-success badge-md \">The Hunchmate Protocol</span><h2 class=\"section-title\">Simplified Event Lifecycle</h2></div><div class=\"about-lifecycle\"><div class=\"about-lifecycle__step glass\"><span class=\"about-lifecycle__emoji\">🏗️</span><span class=\"about-lifecycle__num\">01</span><h4>Architect</h4><p>Organizers create and publish events with full customization.</p></div><div class=\"about-lifecycle__step glass\"><span class=\"about-lifecycle__emoji\">⚡</span><span class=\"about-lifecycle__num\">02</span><h4>Mobilize</h4><p>Participants discover, register, and receive QR entry passes.</p></div><div class=\"about-lifecycle__step glass\"><span class=\"about-lifecycle__emoji\">🔍</span><span class=\"about-lifecycle__num\">03</span><h4>Validate</h4><p>On event day, QR scanning verifies and tracks attendance instantly.</p></div><div class=\"about-lifecycle__step glass\"><span class=\"about-lifecycle__emoji\">🏆</span><span class=\"about-lifecycle__num\">04</span><h4>Credential</h4><p>Post-event, digital credentials are generated and distributed.</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"about-cta section-lg\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"about-cta__banner glass\"><h2>Ready to Shape the Future?</h2><p>Whether you&#x27;re a participant seeking challenges or an organizer building the next big event — we&#x27;re here for you.</p><div class=\"about-cta__btns\"><a href=\"/events\"><button class=\"btn btn-primary btn-lg   \"><span>Explore Events</span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></button></a><a href=\"/signup\"><button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-lg   \"><span>Get Started</span></button></a></div></div></div></section></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"site-footer\" aria-label=\"Site footer\"><div class=\"site-footer__glow-bar\"></div><div class=\"site-footer__inner container\"><div class=\"site-footer__top\"><div class=\"site-footer__brand-col\"><a class=\"site-footer__brand-logo\" aria-label=\"Hunchmate Home\" href=\"/\"><img src=\"/_next/static/media/HUNCHMATE - Logo Pack (2).0xjy2zfzpq5od.png\" alt=\"HunchMate\"/></a><p class=\"site-footer__tagline\">Discover and attend <br/>the best hackathons &amp; tech events — all in one place.</p><div class=\"site-footer__socials\" aria-label=\"Social links\"><a href=\"https://x.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" class=\"site-footer__social\" aria-label=\"X / Twitter\"><svg 